  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STEALTH DRIVEN ARENA COMBAT</strong> – <strong>Stay hidden</strong>, or risk being exposed. The darkness shields you from view, but <strong>every shot fired reveals your position</strong>, so don’t stay still for long! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/49b6ae4e9620e17d17377bffff1fd861.poster.avif?t=1761538415\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/49b6ae4e9620e17d17377bffff1fd861.webm?t=1761538415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/49b6ae4e9620e17d17377bffff1fd861.mp4?t=1761538415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MULTIPLAYER MAYHEM</strong> – <strong>Battle</strong> with up to 4 friends in a <strong>high-stakes deathmatch</strong>, or play other classic modes like <strong>Capture the Flag</strong>. Only the <strong>craftiest</strong> will dominate! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/77a31d264a7fb343f8d6a25aa74aae28.poster.avif?t=1761538415\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/77a31d264a7fb343f8d6a25aa74aae28.webm?t=1761538415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/77a31d264a7fb343f8d6a25aa74aae28.mp4?t=1761538415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OFFLINE BOTS & CHALLENGE MODE </strong> – Play<strong> </strong>against <strong>bots</strong> or tackle <strong>special challenges</strong> for each weapon to sharpen your skills before facing off in the chaos of live combat. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/01c16e53daa1f94e94e6ba5b86eacbff.poster.avif?t=1761538415\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/01c16e53daa1f94e94e6ba5b86eacbff.webm?t=1761538415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/01c16e53daa1f94e94e6ba5b86eacbff.mp4?t=1761538415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>18 MAPS, 6 EPIC THEMES</strong> – <strong>Conquer diverse maps</strong>, from haunted mansions to neon-lit discos, each packed with <strong>unique light mechanics</strong>. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/4aa642611f24de5dcff8be1bd8a45e16.poster.avif?t=1761538415\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/4aa642611f24de5dcff8be1bd8a45e16.webm?t=1761538415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419700/extras/4aa642611f24de5dcff8be1bd8a45e16.mp4?t=1761538415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
